===  Access ===
* About 15 minutes on foot from {{ill|lt=JR West|Q502125|WD=Q502125|lt=JR West|1=West Japan Railway Company}} / {{ill|lt=Kintetsu Railway|Q1531085|WD=Q1531085|lt=Kintetsu|1=Kintetsu Railway}} {{ill|lt=Sakurai Station (Nara)|Q5361714|WD=Q5361714|lt=Sakurai Station|1=Sakurai Station (Nara)}}
* From JR/Kintetsu Sakurai Station, bus for {{ill|lt=Tanzan Shrine|Q488618|WD=Q488618|1=Tanzan Shrine}}, get off at "Kaminomori-chō," then 2 minutes on foot

